## Database Advisors — Run These First

Supabase has two built-in automated advisors that scan your database and flag problems. Always run these on a new project before spending time debugging.

```
Supabase Dashboard → Advisors

Security Advisor — finds:
  - Tables with RLS disabled
  - Functions with SECURITY DEFINER but no search_path set
  - Roles with excessive privileges
  - Publicly accessible tables without policies

Performance Advisor — finds:
  - Foreign key columns without an index (common cause of slow queries)
  - Duplicate indexes
  - Tables that could benefit from BRIN indexes (time-series)
  - Unused indexes (wasting write performance)
```

**Every Rocket project: run both advisors before first deploy. Fix everything flagged in Security Advisor. Fix the high-impact items from Performance Advisor.**

